    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this impeccably preserved specimen. Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle has been curated for the most discerning collector, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a testament to meticulous stewardship and an investment-grade opportunity for its next owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
